PURCHASES.LABEL: Total Purchases
PURCHASES.TOOLTIP: Total purchase revenue per period (day, week, month) in the selected timeframe

ORDERS.LABEL: Total Orders
ORDERS.TOOLTIP: Number of successful orders executed in each period (day, week, month) by order type

TOOLTIP.LABEL: Status of the inventory (average over time)

TYPES.FULL: Number of lanes which have more than 40 % capacity filled with products
TYPES.LOW: Number of lanes which have at least one but less than 40 % capacity filled with products
TYPES.EMPTY: Number of lanes which have 0 (zero) products in

TOP_PRODUCTS.LABEL: Most Popular Products
TOP_PRODUCTS.TOOLTIP: Most sold products by numbers (quantity) purchased during the whole timeframe. The sum shows the overall revenue achieved with this product in the whole timeframe

SUM.LABEL: Total Revenue
SUM.TOOLTIP: Total amount of revenue generated during the whole timeframe (sum of all purchases)

AVG_REVENUE_PER_PERIOD.LABEL: Average Revenue Per Period
AVG_REVENUE_PER_PERIOD.TOOLTIP: Average revenue per period (day / week / month) achieved during the timeframe (sum of all purchases divided by number of periods)

AVG_TOTAL_PRICE.LABEL: Average Purchase Total Price
AVG_TOTAL_PRICE.TOOLTIP: Average revenue achieved per purchase done (orders without a purchase are excluded)

AVG_TOTAL_QUANTITY.LABEL: Average Purchase Total Quantity
AVG_TOTAL_QUANTITY.TOOLTIP: Average number of products per purchase (orders without a purchase are excluded)

TOTAL_MINIBAR_ORDERS.LABEL: Total No. Minibar Orders
TOTAL_MINIBAR_ORDERS.TOOLTIP: Number of minibar orders during the whole timeframe

TOTAL_ROOM_SERVICE_ORDERS.LABEL: Total No. Room Service Orders
TOTAL_ROOM_SERVICE_ORDERS.TOOLTIP: Number of room service orders during the whole timeframe

AVG_MINIBAR_ORDERS.LABEL: Average No. Minibar Orders
AVG_MINIBAR_ORDERS.TOOLTIP: Average number of minibar orders per period (day / week / month), calculated by overall number of orders divided by number of periods

AVG_ROOM_SERVICE_ORDERS.LABEL: Average No. Room Service Orders
AVG_ROOM_SERVICE_ORDERS.TOOLTIP: Average number of room service orders per period (day / week / month), calculated by overall number of orders divided by number of periods
